info.senderName: NWS Duluth (Northeast Minnesota and Northern Wisconsin)
info.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued September 09 at 10:44PM CDT until September 10 at 9:00AM CDT by NWS Duluth
info.description: ...DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM CDT SATURDAY... * WHAT...Visibility less than 1/4 mile in dense fog. * WHERE...In Minnesota, Carlton and South St. Louis and Pine Counties. In Wisconsin, Douglas and Burnett Counties. This includes the Tribal Lands of the Fond du Lac Band and the Mille Lacs Band, Hinckley and, Lena Lake areas. * WHEN...Until 9 AM CDT Saturday. * IMPACTS...Hazardous driving conditions due to low visibility. * ADDITIONAL DETAILS...If you are traveling, you may noticed abrupt changes, both better and worse, in visibility. Be prepared for changing conditions.
info.instruction: If driving, slow down, use your headlights, and leave plenty of distance ahead of you.
